# Evohome Command Hunting
# Author: Evsdd (2017)
# Python 2.7.11
# Requires pyserial module which can be installed using 'python -m pip install pyserial'
# A simple Windows Python script to hunt for recognised Evohome RQ/RP commands
# The program sends every possible RQ command 0x0000-0xFFFF with a payload of 01 to the specified controller
# If a RQ is received within the next 3 messages the command is logged.
